Description: 5 of the COOLEST Heirlooms in Apex Legends! Apex Legends News. Apex Leaks.  Heirloom and Artifacts are what every player of Apex Legends wants to have for their Legend. Whether it's Revenant's Scythe, Fuse's Guitar, Horizon's Gravity Maw, Octane's Butterfly Knife, or the Katar Artifact, Apex Legends has a bunch of Heirlooms to choose from.  With R5 Reloaded, a modded version of Apex Legends, players can create their own Heirlooms and models, such as a Ballistic Knife, Wolverine Claws, Warhammer, and so much more!
